        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6288",
        "content": "The town, aware now of the stupendous change that had come to the fortunes of the Burton family, stared, gossiped, shook wise heads of prophecy, then passed on to the next sensation-which happened to be the return of four soldiers from across the seas; three crippled, one blinded.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
